<script type="text/javascript">

var initdefaultregion = false;
function initDefaultRegion(){	
	if($('#regionLabel').length > 0){
    	initdefaultregion = true;
        $('#regionLabel').val('Ulyanovsk, 81');
        $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search');
    } 
	
}
var isMobileDevice=false;
//var overrideByRegionNum=false;
var isRegionAutoCompleteInitialized=false;
var workingDomain='thebluebook.com';
var pageid = 856;
showregionlist = 0;
currentsearch = '';
searchtermkeypresscheck = 0;
openpopularregions = 0;
regionRequestComplete = 0;
var VendorCheck = [];

//Android Viewport height fix
var isAndroid = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("android") > -1; //&& ua.indexOf("mobile"); 
if (isAndroid) {
    document.write('<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,height=' + window.innerHeight + ', initial-scale=1.0">');
}


$('#searchFrm').on('submit', function () {
    ga('send', 'event', 'Search', 'Click', 'Search BlueBook');
});

$('#searchTerm').on('keyup', function () {
    var term = $('#searchTerm').val();
    if (term !== '') {
        //console.log(term);
        completeSearchTerm();
    }
});

function showSearchKewordAlert() {
    if (workingDomain == 'bidscope.com' || workingDomain == 'www.bidscope.com' || workingDomain == 'www.oneteam.build' || workingDomain == 'oneteam.build') {
        workingDomain = "www.thebluebook.com";
    }
    BootstrapDialog.alert({
        title: 'Looking for Companies or Trades?',
        message: 'To search the most comprehensive database of commercial construction companies please enter a company name or keyword or <a href="http://' + workingDomain + '/?RegionNumber=' + $('#region').val() + '"><strong>click here</strong></a> to find your local Who\'s Who Edition.',
        type: BootstrapDialog.TYPE_PRIMARY, // <-- Default value is BootstrapDialog.TYPE_PRIMARY
        btnOKClass: 'btn-default', // <-- If you didn't specify it, dialog type will be used,
        callback: function (result) {
        }
    });
}



function completeSearchTerm() {
    $("#searchTerm").autocomplete({

        source: function (request, response) {
            $.ajax({
                url: "globalassets/api/public/getdata.php",
                dataType: "jsonp",
                data: {
                    featureClass: "P",
                    style: "full",
                    maxRows: 20,
                    name_startsWith: request.term
                },
                success: function (data) {
                    response($.map(data, function (item) {
                        return {
                            label: item.title,
                            value: item.title,
                            type: item.type,
                            classnum: item.classnum,
                            priority: item.bknum
                        };
                    }));
                }
            });
        },
        minLength: 2,
        select: function (event, ui) {
            $('#searchFrm #class').remove();
            if (ui.item.type == 'CLASS') {
                $('#searchFrm').append('<input type="hidden" id="class" name="class" value="' + ui.item.classnum + '" />');
            }
            $('#search,#searchTerm').val('');
            searchtermkeypresscheck = 0;

            //setTimeout('searchSubmit2016();', 100);
        },
        open: function (event, ui) {
            $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-all").addClass("ui-corner-top search-autocomplete-open");
            $('.ui-autocomplete').off('menufocus hover mouseover mouseenter');
            searchtermkeypresscheck = 1;
        },
        close: function () {
            $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-top").addClass("ui-corner-all").removeClass('search-autocomplete-open');
        }
    }).data("ui-autocomplete")._renderItem = function (ul, item) {
        if ($('.searchTermAutoComplete').length < 1) { ul.addClass('searchTermAutoComplete'); } //Ul custom class here

        item.label = item.label.replace(new RegExp("(?![^&;]+;)(?!<[^<>]*)(" + $.ui.autocomplete.escapeRegex(this.term) + ")(?![^<>]*>)(?![^&;]+;)", "gi"), "<strong>$1</strong>");

        return $('<li class="priority_icon_' + item.type + '" title="' + item.classnum + '">')
            .append('<a><span class="title">' + item.label + '</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span></span></a>')
            .appendTo(ul);
    }
}





function detectswipe(ele, func) {
    return false; //do not use swipe, otherwise can't scroll over menu.

    swipe_det = new Object();
    swipe_det.sX = 0;
    swipe_det.sY = 0;
    swipe_det.eX = 0;
    swipe_det.eY = 0;
    var min_x = 30; //min x swipe for horizontal swipe
    var max_x = 30; //max x difference for vertical swipe
    var min_y = 50; //min y swipe for vertical swipe
    var max_y = 60; //max y difference for horizontal swipe
    var direc = "";
    ele.addEventListener('touchstart', function (e) {
        var t = e.touches[0];
        swipe_det.sX = t.screenX;
        swipe_det.sY = t.screenY;
    }, false);
    ele.addEventListener('touchmove', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var t = e.touches[0];
        swipe_det.eX = t.screenX;
        swipe_det.eY = t.screenY;
    }, false);
    ele.addEventListener('touchend', function (e) {
        //horizontal detection
        if ((((swipe_det.eX - min_x > swipe_det.sX) || (swipe_det.eX + min_x < swipe_det.sX)) && ((swipe_det.eY < swipe_det.sY + max_y) && (swipe_det.sY > swipe_det.eY - max_y) && (swipe_det.eX > 0)))) {
            if (swipe_det.eX > swipe_det.sX) direc = "r";
            else direc = "l";
        }
        //vertical detection
        else if ((((swipe_det.eY - min_y > swipe_det.sY) || (swipe_det.eY + min_y < swipe_det.sY)) && ((swipe_det.eX < swipe_det.sX + max_x) && (swipe_det.sX > swipe_det.eX - max_x) && (swipe_det.eY > 0)))) {
            if (swipe_det.eY > swipe_det.sY) direc = "d";
            else direc = "u";
        }

        if (direc != "") {
            if (typeof func == 'function') func(ele, direc);
        }
        direc = "";
        swipe_det.sX = 0;
        swipe_det.sY = 0;
        swipe_det.eX = 0;
        swipe_det.eY = 0;
    }, false);
}


function initHeaderControl() {
    if ($('body').hasClass('static-collapsed') || $('body').hasClass('yardi-search-results')) {
        $('.header-wrap').addClass('navbar-collapsed');
        $('.navbar-brand').addClass('small-logo');
        return;
    }
    //shrink the header on sroll
    $(window).scroll(function () {
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth > 767 || winWidth < 550) { //apply only if not in mobile mode
            var deviceScrollTop = $(document).scrollTop();
            if ((isMobileDevice && deviceScrollTop > 5) || deviceScrollTop > 50) {
                if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === false && $('#regionLabel.search-autocomplete-open').length < 1) {
                    $('.header-wrap').addClass('navbar-collapsed');
                    $('.navbar-brand').addClass('small-logo');
                }
            } else {
                if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === true) {
                    if ($('#site-navigation').hasClass('in')) {
                        $('.navbar-toggle').click();
                    }
                    $('.header-wrap').removeClass('navbar-collapsed');
                    $('.navbar-brand').removeClass('small-logo');
                }
            }
        }
    });
    //end of shrink the header on sroll

    //open on manufacturer click
    $('.mfg-toggle').find('input').on('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        window.open("http://bpmselect.com");
    });

    //hide mobile menu on click/tap overlay
    $('.mobileMenuDimmed').on('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        $('.navbar-toggle').trigger('blur');
        $(".hamburgerMenu").hide("slide", { direction: "right" }, 200, function () {
            $('.mobileMenuDimmed').hide(100);
        });
    });

    //Hamburger Menu close on mouse out
    $('.navbar-toggle').on('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth > 767 && !isMobileDevice) { //if not in mobile mode show it floating over the hamburger
            var objOffset = $("#login-btn-wrapper").find('button').offset();
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('top', objOffset.top + 'px');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('left', (objOffset.left - 188) + 'px');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").slideDown(200);
        } else {
            var objOffset = $(".header-wrap");
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('top', '0px');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('left', ($(objOffset).width() - ($(".hamburgerMenu").width() + 40)) + 'px');
            $('.mobileMenuDimmed').show(100);
            $(window).scrollTop(0);
            if (isMobileDevice) { //in the case the mobile device width is > 780
                $('.hamburgerMenu').css('height', '100%');
            }
            $(".hamburgerMenu").show("slide", { direction: "right" }, 200);

        }
    });


    $('.hamburgerMenu').on('mouseleave', function (e) {
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth > 767 && !isMobileDevice) { //not mobile?
            e.preventDefault();
            e.stopPropagation();
            $(e.target).removeClass('active');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").slideUp(200);
            $('.navbar-toggle').trigger('blur');
        }
    });



    //end of hamburger menu

    // Explore the network
    var is_over_expnet_submenu = false;
    var is_over_expnet = false;
    var hideexpnetTimer = null;
    var exploreTheNetworkMenuLinkWaitMiliseconds = 400;
    
    /*
    function closeEXPNETMenu() {
        $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').hide();//slideUp(100);
        $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').removeClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
    }
    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('click', function (e) {
        if (e.target.tagName == 'A' || e.target.tagName == 'IMG')
            return true;
        else
            return false;
    });
    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('mousemove', function (e) {
        is_over_expnet_submenu = false;
        is_over_expnet = true;
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);

        if ($('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').hasClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive') == false) {
            setTimeout(function () {
                if (is_over_expnet) {
                    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').show();
                    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').addClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
                }
            }, exploreTheNetworkMenuLinkWaitMiliseconds);
        }
    });
    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('mouseenter', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
        is_over_expnet_submenu = true;
        is_over_expnet = true;
        setTimeout(function () {
            if (is_over_expnet) {
                $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').show();//slideDown(100);
                $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').addClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
            }
        }, exploreTheNetworkMenuLinkWaitMiliseconds);
    });

    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('mouseleave', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        is_over_expnet = false;
        if (!is_over_expnet_submenu || is_over_expnet) {
            //close menu
            $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').hide();//slideUp(100);
            $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').removeClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
        }
        hideexpnetTimer = setTimeout(closeEXPNETMenu(), 2000);
    });
    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').on('mousemove', function (e) {
        is_over_expnet_submenu = true;
        is_over_expnet = false;
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
    });
    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').on('mouseenter', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        is_over_expnet_submenu = true;
        $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').addClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
    });
    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').on('mouseleave', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        is_over_expnet_submenu = false;
        if (!is_over_expnet) {
            $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').slideUp(100);
            $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').removeClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
            hideexpnetTimer = setTimeout(closeEXPNETMenu(), 2000);
        }
    });
*/
    //end of Explore thenetwork
  

    //show/hide search field on mobile when taping the hamburger and showing menu
    $('.navbar-collapse').on('show.bs.collapse', function () {
        $('.hamburgerMenu').addClass('active');
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth < 450) { //apply only if mobile mode
            if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === false) {
                $('.header-wrap').addClass('navbar-collapsed');
            }

        }
    });
    $('.navbar-collapse').on(' hide.bs.collapse', function () {
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        $('.hamburgerMenu').removeClass('active');
        if (winWidth < 450 && $(document).scrollTop() < 51) { //apply only if not in mobile mode
            if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === true) {
                $('.header-wrap').removeClass('navbar-collapsed');
            }
        }
    });
    //end of show/hide search field on mobile
}





function initExitLoader() {
    $(window).bind('beforeunload', function (e) {

        // code to execute when browser is closed
        setTimeout(function () {
            launchLoader();
            $('.ui-widget-overlay').on('click', function () { if ($("#dialog-modal-loader").is(':visible')) { $("#dialog-modal-loader").dialog('close'); } });
            // DESTROY LOADER AFTER 30 SECONDS
            setTimeout(function () { if ($("#dialog-modal-loader").is(':visible')) { $("#dialog-modal-loader").dialog('close'); } }, 30000);
        }, 3000);

    });
}


function initRegionAutoComplete() {
    var autoselecttimer;
    var storedsearch;
    enableAsync = true;
    if ($("#regionLabel").length > 0) {
        isRegionAutoCompleteInitialized = true;
        $("#regionLabel").autocomplete({
            source: function (request, response) {
				if ((!isNaN(request.term) && request.term.length > 4) || (isNaN(request.term) && request.term.length > 2)){
                $.ajax({
                    url: "globalassets/api/public/getLocations.php",
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    data: {
                        maxRows: 20,
                        q: request.term,
                        showregionlist: showregionlist
                    },
                    success: function (data) {
                        if (data.data == null) {
                            showregionlist = 1;
                            $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search', '****');

                        } else {
                            storedsearch = request.term;
                            response($.map(data.data, function (item) {
                                city = '';
                                state = '';
                                regionval = '';
                                booksplitlabel = '';
                                if (item.city != '' && typeof item.city !== 'undefined' && item.city != null) { city = item.city; }
                                if (item.state != '' && typeof item.state !== 'undefined' && item.state != null) { state = ', ' + item.state; }
                                if (item.region != '' && typeof item.region !== 'undefined' && item.region != null) { regionval = item.region; }
                                if (item.booksplitlabel != '' && typeof item.booksplitlabel !== 'undefined' && item.booksplitlabel != null) { booksplitlabel = item.booksplitlabel; }
                                return {
                                    label: city + state,
                                    value: city + state,
                                    region: regionval,
                                    booksplitlabel: booksplitlabel
                                };
                            }));
                        }
                    }
                });
				// END OF 5 NUMERICAL CHECK OR 3 ALPHA CHECK
				}
            },
            minLength: 2,
            delay: 100,
            open: function (event, ui) {
                regionRequestComplete = 0;
                if ($(window).width() < 768) { $(window).scrollTop(0); }
                $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-all").addClass("search-autocomplete-open");
                if (typeof initdefaultregion !== 'undefined' && initdefaultregion == true) {

                    $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click();
                    initdefaultregion = 0;
                }
                // INIT ENTER KEY
                $('#regionLabel').keypress(function (e) {
                    keypresscheck = 1;
                    if (e.which == 13 && $('.regionAutoComplete').is(':visible') && $('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1) {
                        $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click();
                        return false;
                    }
                });

                // CLEAR TIMEOUT EVERYTIME AUTOCOMPLETE OPENS
                clearTimeout(autoselecttimer);
                // IF AUTOCOMPLETE ONLY HAS 1 ITEM START TIMER FOR AUTO SELECT
                if ($('.regionAutoComplete a').length == 1 && keypresscheck) {
                    autoselecttimer = setTimeout(function () {
                        // DOUBLE CHECK THERE IS STILL ONLY 1 ITEM BEFORE AUTOSELECTING
                        if ($('.regionAutoComplete a').length == 1 && $('.regionAutoComplete').is(':visible')) { $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click(); }
                    }, 1000);
                } else {
                    // MORE THAN 1 ITEM CLEAR TIMER
                    clearTimeout(autoselecttimer);
                }
                // FORCE SELECT FIRST ITEM WHEN USER HASNT USED AUTO DROPDOWN
                if ($('#srchBtn').length > 0) {
                    $('#srchBtn').on('focus', function () {
                        if (keypresscheck > 0 && regionRequestComplete != 1) {
                            // PREVENT FORM FROM SUBMITTING
                            $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click();
                            enableAsync = false;
                        }
                    });

                }
            },
            close: function () {
                $(this).removeClass('search-autocomplete-open');
            },
            select: function (event, ui) {
                $('#region').val(ui.item.region);
                $('#geographicarea').remove();
                if (ui.item.booksplitlabel != '' && typeof ui.item.booksplitlabel !== 'undefined') {
                    $('#searchFrm').append('<input type="hidden" name="geographicarea" id="geographicarea" value="' + ui.item.booksplitlabel + '" />');
                }
                // CLEAR keycountarray for autoselect
                keypresscheck = 0;
                $.ajax({
                    method: "GET",
                    url: "/globalassets/tools/api/setSessionLocation.php",
                    xhrFields: {
                        withCredentials: true
                    },
                    async: enableAsync,
                    data: {
                        l: encodeURIComponent(ui.item.value.trim().replace(/,$/g, '')),
                        r: ui.item.region.trim().replace(/,$/g, '')
                    }
                }).done(function (msg) {
                    regionRequestComplete = 1;
                });


                setTimeout(function () { $('#regionLabel').val($('#regionLabel').val().replace(/&amp;/g, '&')).val(); }, 10);
            }
        }).data("ui-autocomplete")._renderItem = function (ul, item) {

            if ($('.regionAutoComplete').length < 1) { ul.addClass('regionAutoComplete dropdown-menu'); } //Ul custom class here

            item.label = item.label.replace('&amp;', '&');
            item.label = item.label.replace(new RegExp("(?![^&;]+;)(?!<[^<>]*)(" + $.ui.autocomplete.escapeRegex(this.term) + ")(?![^<>]*>)(?![^&;]+;)", "gi"), "<strong>$1</strong>");

            if ($('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1 && storedsearch == 'showpopularcities') {
                $('.regionAutoComplete').prepend('<strong class="popularRegionHeader" style="display:block; padding:5px;">Below are the most popular cities.</strong>');
            } else if ($('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1 && showregionlist == 1 && item.label.trim() != 'showpopularcities' && openpopularregions == 1) {
                $('.regionAutoComplete').prepend('<strong class="popularRegionHeader" style="display:block; padding:5px;" onmouseover="$(\'.popularRegionHeader\').removeClass(\'ui-menu-item\'); return false;">Below are the most popular regions.</strong>');
                openpopularregions = 0;
            } else if ($('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1 && showregionlist == 1 && item.label.trim() != 'showpopularcities') {
                $('.regionAutoComplete').prepend('<strong class="popularRegionHeader" style="display:block; padding:5px;" onmouseover="$(\'.popularRegionHeader\').removeClass(\'ui-menu-item\'); return false;">No Results Found.<br />Below are the most popular regions.</strong>');
            } else { showregionlist = 0; }

            return $('<li class="priority_icon_' + item.type + '" title="Region ' + item.region + '">')
                .append('<a><span class="title">' + item.label.trim().replace(/,$/g, '') + '</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span></span></a>')
                .appendTo(ul);

        };
        $('#regionLabel').on('click', function () {
            if ($('#regionLabel').val() == '') {
                openpopularregions = 1;
                $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search', '****').val('').focus();
            } else {
                $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search', $('#regionLabel').val()).focus();
            }
        });
    }

}

function forceSearchFrmSubmission() {
    $("#searchFrm").submit(function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
    });

}

function addFacetToggle() {
    return false;
}

function detectDropDownEdge() {
    setTimeout(function () {
        if ($('.dropdown.open').length > 0) {
            var elm = $('.dropdown.open').find('.dropdown-menu');
            if ($(window).width() < 767 && $('.dropdown.open .action-drop').length > 0) {
                elm.position({
                    of: $('.dropdown.open .action-drop'),
                    my: 'right top',
                    at: 'right bottom'
                });

                $('.pager-wrapper.open .dropdown-menu').css({ 'width': '100%', 'left': '0px' });
            }

        }
    }, 10);
}

function toggleSearchType(srchtype) {
    if (srchtype == 'mfg') {

    }
}

function initSearchTermClearer() {
    if ($('#searchTerm').val() != '') {
        $('.search-term-clearer').removeClass('hide');
    } else {
        $('.search-term-clearer').addClass('hide');
    }

    $('#searchTerm,body').on('keyup mouseup mouseover mouseenter mouseleave blur focus change', function () {
        if ($('#searchTerm').val() != '') {
            $('.search-term-clearer').removeClass('hide');
        } else {
            $('.search-term-clearer').addClass('hide');
        }
    })

    $('#regionLabel,body').on('keyup mouseup mouseover mouseenter mouseleave blur focus change', function () {
        if ($('#regionLabel').val() != '') {
            $('.region-label-clearer').removeClass('hide');
        } else {
            $('.region-label-clearer').addClass('hide');
        }
    });

}


function toggleQuickLinksNav() {
    if ($('.quicklinks-navbar .navbar-collapse li').is(':visible')) {
        $('.quicklinks-navbar .navbar-collapse').addClass('collapse');
    } else {
        $('.quicklinks-navbar .navbar-collapse').removeClass('collapse');
    }
}

function initSubmissionErrorPosition() {
    if ($('.submission-error').is(':visible')) {
        setTimeout(function () { $(window).scrollTop($('.submission-error').offset().top); }, 500);
    }
    if ($('.thanks-title').is(':visible')) {
        setTimeout(function () { $(window).scrollTop($('.thanks-title').offset().top); }, 500);
    }
}

function setLocation(loc, reg) {
    $('#region').val(reg);
    var location = loc.replace(/&amp;/g, '&').replace(' - ', '-');
    $('#regionLabel').val(location);
    if (isRegionAutoCompleteInitialized == false) {
        initRegionAutoComplete();
    }
    $.ajax({
        method: "GET",
        url: "/globalassets/tools/api/setSessionLocation.php",
        xhrFields: {
            withCredentials: true
        },
        data: {
            l: location,
            r: reg
        }
    }).done(function (msg) {

    });
    return true;
}


//if updateDiv is passed as true, and divname contains either a #id or .class 
//it'll try to put the new city name on that div/element
function launchPopularCityModal(divIdOrClass) {
    if ($('#popularCitiesDynamicModal').length > 0) {
        // GET THE DATA
        $.ajax({
            url: "globalassets/api/public/getLocations.php",
            dataType: "jsonp",
            data: {
                maxRows: 20,
                q: 'showpopularcities',
                showregionlist: showregionlist
            },
            success: function (data) {
                popcitycnt = data.data.length;
                popcitymaxcolcnt = 4;
                popcitycolcnt = popcitycnt % popcitymaxcolcnt;
                popcitycurrentcnt = 1;
                popcityoutput = '';
                if (popcitycolcnt == 0) {
                    // EVENLY DISTRIBUTE TO popcitymaxcolcnt COLUMNS
                    popcitymaxcntpercol = Math.floor(popcitycnt / popcitymaxcolcnt);
                } else {
                    popcitymaxcntpercol = Math.floor((popcitycnt / popcitymaxcolcnt) + 1);
                }
                var cityAndState='';
                var currentRegion='';
                var extraFuncsCalls='';
                var eleToUpdate=false;
                if(typeof divIdOrClass !=='undefined' && divIdOrClass!==''){
                    eleToUpdate=true;
                }

                for (i = 0; i < popcitycnt; i++) {
                    //console.log(popcitycurrentcnt);
                    popcitycolstart = '';
                    popcitycolend = '';
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt == 1) {
                        popcitycolstart = '<div class="col-sm-3">';
                    }
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt == popcitymaxcntpercol) {
                        popcitycolend = '</div>';
                    }
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt % 2 == 0) {
                        popcityrowbg = '#f9f9f9;';
                    } else {
                        popcityrowbg = '#fff;';
                    }
                    cityAndState=data.data[i].city + ', ' + data.data[i].state;
                    currentRegion=data.data[i].region;
                    if(eleToUpdate){
                        extraFuncsCalls='changeCityAndRegions(\''+currentRegion+'\',\''+cityAndState+'\'); ';
                    }
                    popcityoutput += popcitycolstart + '<a href="#" style="background:' + 
                                                        popcityrowbg + ' color: #008cba; font-size:16px; display:inline-block; width:100%; padding:3px 3px 3px 10px;" onclick="' + 
                                                        extraFuncsCalls + '$(\'#regionLabel\').val(\'' + cityAndState +
                                                         '\'); $(\'#regionLabel\').autocomplete(\'search\'); keypresscheck = 1; ga(\'send\', \'event\', \'Popular Cities\',\'click\', \'' + 
                                                         cityAndState + '\'); setLocation(\'' + cityAndState + 
                                                         '\',\'' + currentRegion + 
                                                         '\'); $(\'#popularCitiesDynamicModal\').modal(\'hide\'); return false;">' + cityAndState + 
                                                         '</a><br />' + popcitycolend;

                    popcitycurrentcnt++;
                    popcitycolstart = '';
                    popcitycolend = '';
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt > popcitymaxcntpercol) {
                        popcitycurrentcnt = 1;
                    }

                }
                // LAUNCH MODAL HERE
                $('#popularCitiesDynamicModal .modal-body').html('').append('<div><div class="row">' + popcityoutput + '<div></div>');
                $('#popularCitiesDynamicModal').modal();
                $('#popularCitiesDynamicModal').css({
                    'margin-top': $('#main-nav').height(),
                    'z-index': '55555',
                    'position': 'fixed'
                });
            }
        });
    }
}


function addvendorcheck(vendor, isload) {

    if (vendor != '' && typeof vendor !== 'undefined' && vendor != 'null') {
        if (typeof vendor !== 'undefined') {
            vendor = vendor.toString();
        }
        if ($.inArray(vendor, VendorCheck) == -1) { // PUT INTO ARRAY
            VendorCheck.push(vendor);

        }
        else {
            VendorCheck = $.grep(VendorCheck, function (val) { return val != vendor; }); // REMOVE FROM ARRAY

        }

        setCookie('selectedVendors', getselectedvendors(), 90, '');

        updateNumSelected();
    }
}
function getselectedvendors(delim) {
    if (delim == 1) {
        repvendorcheck = VendorCheck.toString().replace(/,/g, ';');
        return repvendorcheck;
    }
    else {
        repvendorcheck = VendorCheck.toString();
        return repvendorcheck;
    }
}



$(document).ready(function () {

    initHeaderControl();
    initRegionAutoComplete();
    initDefaultRegion();
    initSearchTermClearer();
    initSubmissionErrorPosition();
    //
    $('.dropdown-menu.login-dropdown').click(function (event) {
        event.stopPropagation();
    });
    $('.dropdown-toggle').click(function (e) {
        detectDropDownEdge();
        e.preventDefault();
    });
    $('.result_check').each(function () { if ($(this).is(':checked')) { mobileCheckToggle($(this).attr('name').replace('acct', '')); } });

    $('#searchFrm').keypress(function (e) {
        if (e.which == 13) {
            if ($('#searchTerm').val() != '' && $('#regionLabel').val() != '') {
                $('#srchBtn').focus();
                $('#srchBtn')[0].click();
                return false;
            }
        }
    });
    $('#srchBtn').on('focus', function () {
        if (searchtermkeypresscheck == 1) { 
			partialsearchterm = $('#searchTerm').val();
			termsplit = partialsearchterm.split(' ');
				if (termsplit.length < 3){ 
					if ($('.searchTermAutoComplete > li:eq(0)').text().toLowerCase().indexOf(partialsearchterm.toLowerCase()) !== -1){ console.log('match'); $('.searchTermAutoComplete a:first').click(); }
					else { console.log('no match'); }
		}
		}
    });

});

</style><script type="text/javascript">//<![CDATA[

    window.onload=function(){
      
//this is just whats inside the first script tag of the beacon embed cut and pasted into a template string
const beaconInnerScript = `!function(e,t,n){function a(){var e=t.getElementsByTagName("script")[0],n=t.createElement("script");n.type="text/javascript",n.async=!0,n.src="https://beacon-v2.helpscout.net",e.parentNode.insertBefore(n,e)}if(e.Beacon=n=function(t,n,a){e.Beacon.readyQueue.push({method:t,options:n,data:a})},n.readyQueue=[],"complete"===t.readyState)return a();e.attachEvent?e.attachEvent("onload",a):e.addEventListener("load",a,!1)}(window,document,window.Beacon||function(){});`

//this function
const embedBeacon = (beaconId, beaconEmbedScript) => {
	//probably obvious but were just creating a brand new script tag with the innards from the embed
  const newScriptTag = document.createElement('script')
  newScriptTag.text = beaconEmbedScript;
	//then sticking it into the beginning of the head of the page
  document.head.insertBefore(newScriptTag, document.head.firstElementChild);
  //then a standard init call to wake it up
  window.Beacon('init', beaconId)
}

//change the number here to change the timeout
//could also do this in an event listener callback or wherever
setTimeout(() => {
	//call the function with the beacon id
	embedBeacon('3315178a-e4d5-4df2-82df-bdc1035e8064', beaconInnerScript);
}, 3000)


    }

<script type="text/javascript">

var initdefaultregion = false;
function initDefaultRegion(){	
	if($('#regionLabel').length > 0){
    	initdefaultregion = true;
        $('#regionLabel').val('Ulyanovsk, 81');
        $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search');
    } 
	
}
var isMobileDevice=false;
//var overrideByRegionNum=false;
var isRegionAutoCompleteInitialized=false;
var workingDomain='thebluebook.com';
var pageid = 856;
showregionlist = 0;
currentsearch = '';
searchtermkeypresscheck = 0;
openpopularregions = 0;
regionRequestComplete = 0;
var VendorCheck = [];

//Android Viewport height fix
var isAndroid = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("android") > -1; //&& ua.indexOf("mobile"); 
if (isAndroid) {
    document.write('<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,height=' + window.innerHeight + ', initial-scale=1.0">');
}


$('#searchFrm').on('submit', function () {
    ga('send', 'event', 'Search', 'Click', 'Search BlueBook');
});

$('#searchTerm').on('keyup', function () {
    var term = $('#searchTerm').val();
    if (term !== '') {
        //console.log(term);
        completeSearchTerm();
    }
});

function showSearchKewordAlert() {
    if (workingDomain == 'bidscope.com' || workingDomain == 'www.bidscope.com' || workingDomain == 'www.oneteam.build' || workingDomain == 'oneteam.build') {
        workingDomain = "www.thebluebook.com";
    }
    BootstrapDialog.alert({
        title: 'Looking for Companies or Trades?',
        message: 'To search the most comprehensive database of commercial construction companies please enter a company name or keyword or <a href="http://' + workingDomain + '/?RegionNumber=' + $('#region').val() + '"><strong>click here</strong></a> to find your local Who\'s Who Edition.',
        type: BootstrapDialog.TYPE_PRIMARY, // <-- Default value is BootstrapDialog.TYPE_PRIMARY
        btnOKClass: 'btn-default', // <-- If you didn't specify it, dialog type will be used,
        callback: function (result) {
        }
    });
}



function completeSearchTerm() {
    $("#searchTerm").autocomplete({

        source: function (request, response) {
            $.ajax({
                url: "globalassets/api/public/getdata.php",
                dataType: "jsonp",
                data: {
                    featureClass: "P",
                    style: "full",
                    maxRows: 20,
                    name_startsWith: request.term
                },
                success: function (data) {
                    response($.map(data, function (item) {
                        return {
                            label: item.title,
                            value: item.title,
                            type: item.type,
                            classnum: item.classnum,
                            priority: item.bknum
                        };
                    }));
                }
            });
        },
        minLength: 2,
        select: function (event, ui) {
            $('#searchFrm #class').remove();
            if (ui.item.type == 'CLASS') {
                $('#searchFrm').append('<input type="hidden" id="class" name="class" value="' + ui.item.classnum + '" />');
            }
            $('#search,#searchTerm').val('');
            searchtermkeypresscheck = 0;

            //setTimeout('searchSubmit2016();', 100);
        },
        open: function (event, ui) {
            $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-all").addClass("ui-corner-top search-autocomplete-open");
            $('.ui-autocomplete').off('menufocus hover mouseover mouseenter');
            searchtermkeypresscheck = 1;
        },
        close: function () {
            $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-top").addClass("ui-corner-all").removeClass('search-autocomplete-open');
        }
    }).data("ui-autocomplete")._renderItem = function (ul, item) {
        if ($('.searchTermAutoComplete').length < 1) { ul.addClass('searchTermAutoComplete'); } //Ul custom class here

        item.label = item.label.replace(new RegExp("(?![^&;]+;)(?!<[^<>]*)(" + $.ui.autocomplete.escapeRegex(this.term) + ")(?![^<>]*>)(?![^&;]+;)", "gi"), "<strong>$1</strong>");

        return $('<li class="priority_icon_' + item.type + '" title="' + item.classnum + '">')
            .append('<a><span class="title">' + item.label + '</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span></span></a>')
            .appendTo(ul);
    }
}





function detectswipe(ele, func) {
    return false; //do not use swipe, otherwise can't scroll over menu.

    swipe_det = new Object();
    swipe_det.sX = 0;
    swipe_det.sY = 0;
    swipe_det.eX = 0;
    swipe_det.eY = 0;
    var min_x = 30; //min x swipe for horizontal swipe
    var max_x = 30; //max x difference for vertical swipe
    var min_y = 50; //min y swipe for vertical swipe
    var max_y = 60; //max y difference for horizontal swipe
    var direc = "";
    ele.addEventListener('touchstart', function (e) {
        var t = e.touches[0];
        swipe_det.sX = t.screenX;
        swipe_det.sY = t.screenY;
    }, false);
    ele.addEventListener('touchmove', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var t = e.touches[0];
        swipe_det.eX = t.screenX;
        swipe_det.eY = t.screenY;
    }, false);
    ele.addEventListener('touchend', function (e) {
        //horizontal detection
        if ((((swipe_det.eX - min_x > swipe_det.sX) || (swipe_det.eX + min_x < swipe_det.sX)) && ((swipe_det.eY < swipe_det.sY + max_y) && (swipe_det.sY > swipe_det.eY - max_y) && (swipe_det.eX > 0)))) {
            if (swipe_det.eX > swipe_det.sX) direc = "r";
            else direc = "l";
        }
        //vertical detection
        else if ((((swipe_det.eY - min_y > swipe_det.sY) || (swipe_det.eY + min_y < swipe_det.sY)) && ((swipe_det.eX < swipe_det.sX + max_x) && (swipe_det.sX > swipe_det.eX - max_x) && (swipe_det.eY > 0)))) {
            if (swipe_det.eY > swipe_det.sY) direc = "d";
            else direc = "u";
        }

        if (direc != "") {
            if (typeof func == 'function') func(ele, direc);
        }
        direc = "";
        swipe_det.sX = 0;
        swipe_det.sY = 0;
        swipe_det.eX = 0;
        swipe_det.eY = 0;
    }, false);
}


function initHeaderControl() {
    if ($('body').hasClass('static-collapsed') || $('body').hasClass('yardi-search-results')) {
        $('.header-wrap').addClass('navbar-collapsed');
        $('.navbar-brand').addClass('small-logo');
        return;
    }
    //shrink the header on sroll
    $(window).scroll(function () {
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth > 767 || winWidth < 550) { //apply only if not in mobile mode
            var deviceScrollTop = $(document).scrollTop();
            if ((isMobileDevice && deviceScrollTop > 5) || deviceScrollTop > 50) {
                if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === false && $('#regionLabel.search-autocomplete-open').length < 1) {
                    $('.header-wrap').addClass('navbar-collapsed');
                    $('.navbar-brand').addClass('small-logo');
                }
            } else {
                if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === true) {
                    if ($('#site-navigation').hasClass('in')) {
                        $('.navbar-toggle').click();
                    }
                    $('.header-wrap').removeClass('navbar-collapsed');
                    $('.navbar-brand').removeClass('small-logo');
                }
            }
        }
    });
    //end of shrink the header on sroll

    //open on manufacturer click
    $('.mfg-toggle').find('input').on('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        window.open("http://bpmselect.com");
    });

    //hide mobile menu on click/tap overlay
    $('.mobileMenuDimmed').on('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        $('.navbar-toggle').trigger('blur');
        $(".hamburgerMenu").hide("slide", { direction: "right" }, 200, function () {
            $('.mobileMenuDimmed').hide(100);
        });
    });

    //Hamburger Menu close on mouse out
    $('.navbar-toggle').on('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth > 767 && !isMobileDevice) { //if not in mobile mode show it floating over the hamburger
            var objOffset = $("#login-btn-wrapper").find('button').offset();
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('top', objOffset.top + 'px');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('left', (objOffset.left - 188) + 'px');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").slideDown(200);
        } else {
            var objOffset = $(".header-wrap");
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('top', '0px');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").css('left', ($(objOffset).width() - ($(".hamburgerMenu").width() + 40)) + 'px');
            $('.mobileMenuDimmed').show(100);
            $(window).scrollTop(0);
            if (isMobileDevice) { //in the case the mobile device width is > 780
                $('.hamburgerMenu').css('height', '100%');
            }
            $(".hamburgerMenu").show("slide", { direction: "right" }, 200);

        }
    });


    $('.hamburgerMenu').on('mouseleave', function (e) {
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth > 767 && !isMobileDevice) { //not mobile?
            e.preventDefault();
            e.stopPropagation();
            $(e.target).removeClass('active');
            $(".hamburgerMenu").slideUp(200);
            $('.navbar-toggle').trigger('blur');
        }
    });



    //end of hamburger menu

    // Explore the network
    var is_over_expnet_submenu = false;
    var is_over_expnet = false;
    var hideexpnetTimer = null;
    var exploreTheNetworkMenuLinkWaitMiliseconds = 400;
    
    /*
    function closeEXPNETMenu() {
        $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').hide();//slideUp(100);
        $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').removeClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
    }
    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('click', function (e) {
        if (e.target.tagName == 'A' || e.target.tagName == 'IMG')
            return true;
        else
            return false;
    });
    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('mousemove', function (e) {
        is_over_expnet_submenu = false;
        is_over_expnet = true;
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);

        if ($('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').hasClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive') == false) {
            setTimeout(function () {
                if (is_over_expnet) {
                    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').show();
                    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').addClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
                }
            }, exploreTheNetworkMenuLinkWaitMiliseconds);
        }
    });
    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('mouseenter', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
        is_over_expnet_submenu = true;
        is_over_expnet = true;
        setTimeout(function () {
            if (is_over_expnet) {
                $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').show();//slideDown(100);
                $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').addClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
            }
        }, exploreTheNetworkMenuLinkWaitMiliseconds);
    });

    $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').on('mouseleave', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        is_over_expnet = false;
        if (!is_over_expnet_submenu || is_over_expnet) {
            //close menu
            $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').hide();//slideUp(100);
            $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').removeClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
        }
        hideexpnetTimer = setTimeout(closeEXPNETMenu(), 2000);
    });
    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').on('mousemove', function (e) {
        is_over_expnet_submenu = true;
        is_over_expnet = false;
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
    });
    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').on('mouseenter', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        is_over_expnet_submenu = true;
        $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').addClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
        clearTimeout(hideexpnetTimer);
    });
    $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').on('mouseleave', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        is_over_expnet_submenu = false;
        if (!is_over_expnet) {
            $('.sbmnExploreTheNetwork').slideUp(100);
            $('#exploreTheNetworkMenuLink').removeClass('mnExploreTheNetworkActive');
            hideexpnetTimer = setTimeout(closeEXPNETMenu(), 2000);
        }
    });
*/
    //end of Explore thenetwork
  

    //show/hide search field on mobile when taping the hamburger and showing menu
    $('.navbar-collapse').on('show.bs.collapse', function () {
        $('.hamburgerMenu').addClass('active');
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        if (winWidth < 450) { //apply only if mobile mode
            if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === false) {
                $('.header-wrap').addClass('navbar-collapsed');
            }

        }
    });
    $('.navbar-collapse').on(' hide.bs.collapse', function () {
        var winWidth = $(window).width();
        $('.hamburgerMenu').removeClass('active');
        if (winWidth < 450 && $(document).scrollTop() < 51) { //apply only if not in mobile mode
            if ($('.header-wrap').hasClass('navbar-collapsed') === true) {
                $('.header-wrap').removeClass('navbar-collapsed');
            }
        }
    });
    //end of show/hide search field on mobile
}





function initExitLoader() {
    $(window).bind('beforeunload', function (e) {

        // code to execute when browser is closed
        setTimeout(function () {
            launchLoader();
            $('.ui-widget-overlay').on('click', function () { if ($("#dialog-modal-loader").is(':visible')) { $("#dialog-modal-loader").dialog('close'); } });
            // DESTROY LOADER AFTER 30 SECONDS
            setTimeout(function () { if ($("#dialog-modal-loader").is(':visible')) { $("#dialog-modal-loader").dialog('close'); } }, 30000);
        }, 3000);

    });
}


function initRegionAutoComplete() {
    var autoselecttimer;
    var storedsearch;
    enableAsync = true;
    if ($("#regionLabel").length > 0) {
        isRegionAutoCompleteInitialized = true;
        $("#regionLabel").autocomplete({
            source: function (request, response) {
				if ((!isNaN(request.term) && request.term.length > 4) || (isNaN(request.term) && request.term.length > 2)){
                $.ajax({
                    url: "globalassets/api/public/getLocations.php",
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    data: {
                        maxRows: 20,
                        q: request.term,
                        showregionlist: showregionlist
                    },
                    success: function (data) {
                        if (data.data == null) {
                            showregionlist = 1;
                            $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search', '****');

                        } else {
                            storedsearch = request.term;
                            response($.map(data.data, function (item) {
                                city = '';
                                state = '';
                                regionval = '';
                                booksplitlabel = '';
                                if (item.city != '' && typeof item.city !== 'undefined' && item.city != null) { city = item.city; }
                                if (item.state != '' && typeof item.state !== 'undefined' && item.state != null) { state = ', ' + item.state; }
                                if (item.region != '' && typeof item.region !== 'undefined' && item.region != null) { regionval = item.region; }
                                if (item.booksplitlabel != '' && typeof item.booksplitlabel !== 'undefined' && item.booksplitlabel != null) { booksplitlabel = item.booksplitlabel; }
                                return {
                                    label: city + state,
                                    value: city + state,
                                    region: regionval,
                                    booksplitlabel: booksplitlabel
                                };
                            }));
                        }
                    }
                });
				// END OF 5 NUMERICAL CHECK OR 3 ALPHA CHECK
				}
            },
            minLength: 2,
            delay: 100,
            open: function (event, ui) {
                regionRequestComplete = 0;
                if ($(window).width() < 768) { $(window).scrollTop(0); }
                $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-all").addClass("search-autocomplete-open");
                if (typeof initdefaultregion !== 'undefined' && initdefaultregion == true) {

                    $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click();
                    initdefaultregion = 0;
                }
                // INIT ENTER KEY
                $('#regionLabel').keypress(function (e) {
                    keypresscheck = 1;
                    if (e.which == 13 && $('.regionAutoComplete').is(':visible') && $('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1) {
                        $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click();
                        return false;
                    }
                });

                // CLEAR TIMEOUT EVERYTIME AUTOCOMPLETE OPENS
                clearTimeout(autoselecttimer);
                // IF AUTOCOMPLETE ONLY HAS 1 ITEM START TIMER FOR AUTO SELECT
                if ($('.regionAutoComplete a').length == 1 && keypresscheck) {
                    autoselecttimer = setTimeout(function () {
                        // DOUBLE CHECK THERE IS STILL ONLY 1 ITEM BEFORE AUTOSELECTING
                        if ($('.regionAutoComplete a').length == 1 && $('.regionAutoComplete').is(':visible')) { $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click(); }
                    }, 1000);
                } else {
                    // MORE THAN 1 ITEM CLEAR TIMER
                    clearTimeout(autoselecttimer);
                }
                // FORCE SELECT FIRST ITEM WHEN USER HASNT USED AUTO DROPDOWN
                if ($('#srchBtn').length > 0) {
                    $('#srchBtn').on('focus', function () {
                        if (keypresscheck > 0 && regionRequestComplete != 1) {
                            // PREVENT FORM FROM SUBMITTING
                            $('.regionAutoComplete a:first').click();
                            enableAsync = false;
                        }
                    });

                }
            },
            close: function () {
                $(this).removeClass('search-autocomplete-open');
            },
            select: function (event, ui) {
                $('#region').val(ui.item.region);
                $('#geographicarea').remove();
                if (ui.item.booksplitlabel != '' && typeof ui.item.booksplitlabel !== 'undefined') {
                    $('#searchFrm').append('<input type="hidden" name="geographicarea" id="geographicarea" value="' + ui.item.booksplitlabel + '" />');
                }
                // CLEAR keycountarray for autoselect
                keypresscheck = 0;
                $.ajax({
                    method: "GET",
                    url: "/globalassets/tools/api/setSessionLocation.php",
                    xhrFields: {
                        withCredentials: true
                    },
                    async: enableAsync,
                    data: {
                        l: encodeURIComponent(ui.item.value.trim().replace(/,$/g, '')),
                        r: ui.item.region.trim().replace(/,$/g, '')
                    }
                }).done(function (msg) {
                    regionRequestComplete = 1;
                });


                setTimeout(function () { $('#regionLabel').val($('#regionLabel').val().replace(/&amp;/g, '&')).val(); }, 10);
            }
        }).data("ui-autocomplete")._renderItem = function (ul, item) {

            if ($('.regionAutoComplete').length < 1) { ul.addClass('regionAutoComplete dropdown-menu'); } //Ul custom class here

            item.label = item.label.replace('&amp;', '&');
            item.label = item.label.replace(new RegExp("(?![^&;]+;)(?!<[^<>]*)(" + $.ui.autocomplete.escapeRegex(this.term) + ")(?![^<>]*>)(?![^&;]+;)", "gi"), "<strong>$1</strong>");

            if ($('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1 && storedsearch == 'showpopularcities') {
                $('.regionAutoComplete').prepend('<strong class="popularRegionHeader" style="display:block; padding:5px;">Below are the most popular cities.</strong>');
            } else if ($('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1 && showregionlist == 1 && item.label.trim() != 'showpopularcities' && openpopularregions == 1) {
                $('.regionAutoComplete').prepend('<strong class="popularRegionHeader" style="display:block; padding:5px;" onmouseover="$(\'.popularRegionHeader\').removeClass(\'ui-menu-item\'); return false;">Below are the most popular regions.</strong>');
                openpopularregions = 0;
            } else if ($('.popularRegionHeader').length < 1 && showregionlist == 1 && item.label.trim() != 'showpopularcities') {
                $('.regionAutoComplete').prepend('<strong class="popularRegionHeader" style="display:block; padding:5px;" onmouseover="$(\'.popularRegionHeader\').removeClass(\'ui-menu-item\'); return false;">No Results Found.<br />Below are the most popular regions.</strong>');
            } else { showregionlist = 0; }

            return $('<li class="priority_icon_' + item.type + '" title="Region ' + item.region + '">')
                .append('<a><span class="title">' + item.label.trim().replace(/,$/g, '') + '</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span></span></a>')
                .appendTo(ul);

        };
        $('#regionLabel').on('click', function () {
            if ($('#regionLabel').val() == '') {
                openpopularregions = 1;
                $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search', '****').val('').focus();
            } else {
                $('#regionLabel').autocomplete('search', $('#regionLabel').val()).focus();
            }
        });
    }

}

function forceSearchFrmSubmission() {
    $("#searchFrm").submit(function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
    });

}

function addFacetToggle() {
    return false;
}

function detectDropDownEdge() {
    setTimeout(function () {
        if ($('.dropdown.open').length > 0) {
            var elm = $('.dropdown.open').find('.dropdown-menu');
            if ($(window).width() < 767 && $('.dropdown.open .action-drop').length > 0) {
                elm.position({
                    of: $('.dropdown.open .action-drop'),
                    my: 'right top',
                    at: 'right bottom'
                });

                $('.pager-wrapper.open .dropdown-menu').css({ 'width': '100%', 'left': '0px' });
            }

        }
    }, 10);
}

function toggleSearchType(srchtype) {
    if (srchtype == 'mfg') {

    }
}

function initSearchTermClearer() {
    if ($('#searchTerm').val() != '') {
        $('.search-term-clearer').removeClass('hide');
    } else {
        $('.search-term-clearer').addClass('hide');
    }

    $('#searchTerm,body').on('keyup mouseup mouseover mouseenter mouseleave blur focus change', function () {
        if ($('#searchTerm').val() != '') {
            $('.search-term-clearer').removeClass('hide');
        } else {
            $('.search-term-clearer').addClass('hide');
        }
    })

    $('#regionLabel,body').on('keyup mouseup mouseover mouseenter mouseleave blur focus change', function () {
        if ($('#regionLabel').val() != '') {
            $('.region-label-clearer').removeClass('hide');
        } else {
            $('.region-label-clearer').addClass('hide');
        }
    });

}


function toggleQuickLinksNav() {
    if ($('.quicklinks-navbar .navbar-collapse li').is(':visible')) {
        $('.quicklinks-navbar .navbar-collapse').addClass('collapse');
    } else {
        $('.quicklinks-navbar .navbar-collapse').removeClass('collapse');
    }
}

function initSubmissionErrorPosition() {
    if ($('.submission-error').is(':visible')) {
        setTimeout(function () { $(window).scrollTop($('.submission-error').offset().top); }, 500);
    }
    if ($('.thanks-title').is(':visible')) {
        setTimeout(function () { $(window).scrollTop($('.thanks-title').offset().top); }, 500);
    }
}

function setLocation(loc, reg) {
    $('#region').val(reg);
    var location = loc.replace(/&amp;/g, '&').replace(' - ', '-');
    $('#regionLabel').val(location);
    if (isRegionAutoCompleteInitialized == false) {
        initRegionAutoComplete();
    }
    $.ajax({
        method: "GET",
        url: "/globalassets/tools/api/setSessionLocation.php",
        xhrFields: {
            withCredentials: true
        },
        data: {
            l: location,
            r: reg
        }
    }).done(function (msg) {

    });
    return true;
}


//if updateDiv is passed as true, and divname contains either a #id or .class 
//it'll try to put the new city name on that div/element
function launchPopularCityModal(divIdOrClass) {
    if ($('#popularCitiesDynamicModal').length > 0) {
        // GET THE DATA
        $.ajax({
            url: "globalassets/api/public/getLocations.php",
            dataType: "jsonp",
            data: {
                maxRows: 20,
                q: 'showpopularcities',
                showregionlist: showregionlist
            },
            success: function (data) {
                popcitycnt = data.data.length;
                popcitymaxcolcnt = 4;
                popcitycolcnt = popcitycnt % popcitymaxcolcnt;
                popcitycurrentcnt = 1;
                popcityoutput = '';
                if (popcitycolcnt == 0) {
                    // EVENLY DISTRIBUTE TO popcitymaxcolcnt COLUMNS
                    popcitymaxcntpercol = Math.floor(popcitycnt / popcitymaxcolcnt);
                } else {
                    popcitymaxcntpercol = Math.floor((popcitycnt / popcitymaxcolcnt) + 1);
                }
                var cityAndState='';
                var currentRegion='';
                var extraFuncsCalls='';
                var eleToUpdate=false;
                if(typeof divIdOrClass !=='undefined' && divIdOrClass!==''){
                    eleToUpdate=true;
                }

                for (i = 0; i < popcitycnt; i++) {
                    //console.log(popcitycurrentcnt);
                    popcitycolstart = '';
                    popcitycolend = '';
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt == 1) {
                        popcitycolstart = '<div class="col-sm-3">';
                    }
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt == popcitymaxcntpercol) {
                        popcitycolend = '</div>';
                    }
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt % 2 == 0) {
                        popcityrowbg = '#f9f9f9;';
                    } else {
                        popcityrowbg = '#fff;';
                    }
                    cityAndState=data.data[i].city + ', ' + data.data[i].state;
                    currentRegion=data.data[i].region;
                    if(eleToUpdate){
                        extraFuncsCalls='changeCityAndRegions(\''+currentRegion+'\',\''+cityAndState+'\'); ';
                    }
                    popcityoutput += popcitycolstart + '<a href="#" style="background:' + 
                                                        popcityrowbg + ' color: #008cba; font-size:16px; display:inline-block; width:100%; padding:3px 3px 3px 10px;" onclick="' + 
                                                        extraFuncsCalls + '$(\'#regionLabel\').val(\'' + cityAndState +
                                                         '\'); $(\'#regionLabel\').autocomplete(\'search\'); keypresscheck = 1; ga(\'send\', \'event\', \'Popular Cities\',\'click\', \'' + 
                                                         cityAndState + '\'); setLocation(\'' + cityAndState + 
                                                         '\',\'' + currentRegion + 
                                                         '\'); $(\'#popularCitiesDynamicModal\').modal(\'hide\'); return false;">' + cityAndState + 
                                                         '</a><br />' + popcitycolend;

                    popcitycurrentcnt++;
                    popcitycolstart = '';
                    popcitycolend = '';
                    if (popcitycurrentcnt > popcitymaxcntpercol) {
                        popcitycurrentcnt = 1;
                    }

                }
                // LAUNCH MODAL HERE
                $('#popularCitiesDynamicModal .modal-body').html('').append('<div><div class="row">' + popcityoutput + '<div></div>');
                $('#popularCitiesDynamicModal').modal();
                $('#popularCitiesDynamicModal').css({
                    'margin-top': $('#main-nav').height(),
                    'z-index': '55555',
                    'position': 'fixed'
                });
            }
        });
    }
}


function addvendorcheck(vendor, isload) {

    if (vendor != '' && typeof vendor !== 'undefined' && vendor != 'null') {
        if (typeof vendor !== 'undefined') {
            vendor = vendor.toString();
        }
        if ($.inArray(vendor, VendorCheck) == -1) { // PUT INTO ARRAY
            VendorCheck.push(vendor);

        }
        else {
            VendorCheck = $.grep(VendorCheck, function (val) { return val != vendor; }); // REMOVE FROM ARRAY

        }

        setCookie('selectedVendors', getselectedvendors(), 90, '');

        updateNumSelected();
    }
}
function getselectedvendors(delim) {
    if (delim == 1) {
        repvendorcheck = VendorCheck.toString().replace(/,/g, ';');
        return repvendorcheck;
    }
    else {
        repvendorcheck = VendorCheck.toString();
        return repvendorcheck;
    }
}



$(document).ready(function () {

    initHeaderControl();
    initRegionAutoComplete();
    initDefaultRegion();
    initSearchTermClearer();
    initSubmissionErrorPosition();
    //
    $('.dropdown-menu.login-dropdown').click(function (event) {
        event.stopPropagation();
    });
    $('.dropdown-toggle').click(function (e) {
        detectDropDownEdge();
        e.preventDefault();
    });
    $('.result_check').each(function () { if ($(this).is(':checked')) { mobileCheckToggle($(this).attr('name').replace('acct', '')); } });

    $('#searchFrm').keypress(function (e) {
        if (e.which == 13) {
            if ($('#searchTerm').val() != '' && $('#regionLabel').val() != '') {
                $('#srchBtn').focus();
                $('#srchBtn')[0].click();
                return false;
            }
        }
    });
    $('#srchBtn').on('focus', function () {
        if (searchtermkeypresscheck == 1) { 
			partialsearchterm = $('#searchTerm').val();
			termsplit = partialsearchterm.split(' ');
				if (termsplit.length < 3){ 
					if ($('.searchTermAutoComplete > li:eq(0)').text().toLowerCase().indexOf(partialsearchterm.toLowerCase()) !== -1){ console.log('match'); $('.searchTermAutoComplete a:first').click(); }
					else { console.log('no match'); }
		}
		}
    });

});

</style><script type="text/javascript">//<![CDATA[

    window.onload=function(){
      
//this is just whats inside the first script tag of the beacon embed cut and pasted into a template string
const beaconInnerScript = `!function(e,t,n){function a(){var e=t.getElementsByTagName("script")[0],n=t.createElement("script");n.type="text/javascript",n.async=!0,n.src="https://beacon-v2.helpscout.net",e.parentNode.insertBefore(n,e)}if(e.Beacon=n=function(t,n,a){e.Beacon.readyQueue.push({method:t,options:n,data:a})},n.readyQueue=[],"complete"===t.readyState)return a();e.attachEvent?e.attachEvent("onload",a):e.addEventListener("load",a,!1)}(window,document,window.Beacon||function(){});`

//this function
const embedBeacon = (beaconId, beaconEmbedScript) => {
	//probably obvious but were just creating a brand new script tag with the innards from the embed
  const newScriptTag = document.createElement('script')
  newScriptTag.text = beaconEmbedScript;
	//then sticking it into the beginning of the head of the page
  document.head.insertBefore(newScriptTag, document.head.firstElementChild);
  //then a standard init call to wake it up
  window.Beacon('init', beaconId)
}

//change the number here to change the timeout
//could also do this in an event listener callback or wherever
setTimeout(() => {
	//call the function with the beacon id
	embedBeacon('3315178a-e4d5-4df2-82df-bdc1035e8064', beaconInnerScript);
}, 3000)


    }
